---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import RightColumnCard from '../../layouts/RightColumnCard.astro';

const { class: className } = Astro.props;
---

<RightColumnCard title='Apoyar' headingId='apoyar-title' class={className}>
  <section class:list={['card', className]} aria-labelledby='apoyar-heading'>
    <div>
      <p>
        Si estos acordes te han servido para echar un ratito, puedes echarnos una manita <strong
          >donando</strong
        > con los botones de abajo.
      </p>
      <p>Â¡Gracias por ayudar a que siga subiendo mÃ¡s coplas! ðŸ’œ</p>
    </div>

    <div class='actions' role='group' aria-label='Opciones de apoyo'>
      <a
        href='https://www.buymeacoffee.com/AcordesGaditanos'
        target='_blank'
        rel='noopener noreferrer'
        class='btn'
        data-ga-event='support_bmc_click'
        data-ga-params='{"method":"buymeacoffee"}'>
        <span class='btn__icon'>
          <Icon name='buy-me-a-coffee' width={20} height={28} />
        </span>
        <span class='btn__text'>Buy me a coffee</span>
      </a>

      <a
        href='https://www.paypal.com/donate?business=acordesgaditanos@gmail.com&currency_code=EUR'
        target='_blank'
        rel='noopener noreferrer'
        class='btn btn--paypal'
        data-ga-event='support_paypal_click'
        data-ga-params='{"method":"paypal","currency":"EUR"}'>
        <span class='btn__icon'>
          <Icon name='paypal' width={20} height={20} />
        </span>
        <span class='btn__text'>Paypal</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</RightColumnCard>

<style>
  /* Layout */
  section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--card-background-color);
    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    min-height: 44px;
    flex: 1;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;

    &:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    &.btn--paypal {
      background-color: var(--primary-contrast-color);
      color: var(--primary-color);
    }

    &__icon {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      line-height: 1;
      font-size: 18px;

      & svg {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
      }
    }

    &__text {
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 1.25px;
    }
  }
</style>
